<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --color-primary: #2E4F40;
            --color-secondary: #1a2b22;
            --color-text: #F5F2EC;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--color-primary), var(--color-secondary));
            color: var(--color-text);
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            width: 100%;
            min-height: 100dvh;
        }

        main {
            width: 90%;
            height: 100%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .welcome {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            height: 100%;
            gap: 5px;

            h1 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }

            p {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
                color: var(--color-text-secondary);
            }
        }

        .state-session {
            width: fit-content;
            background: rgba(26, 43, 34, 0.6);
            border: 1px solid rgba(214, 232, 227, 0.1);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            font-weight: 500;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            margin: 30px auto;
        }

        #state {
            color: #4ade80;
            background: rgba(74, 222, 128, 0.1);
            padding: 6px 16px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }

        .inactive-session {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            height: 100%;
            width: 400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: var(--color-secondary);
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            padding: 20px;
            gap: 5px;

            h3 {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }

            p {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
                color: var(--color-text-secondary);
            }
        }

        #btn-log {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            border: none;
            background-color: var(--color-primary);
            color: var(--color-text);
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            text-align: center;
            transition: background-color 0.2s ease-out;
        }

        #btn-log:hover {
            background-color: var(--color-secondary);
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <main>
        <section class="welcome">
            <h1>Bienvenido al panel principal</h1>
            <p>Aqui podras gestionar el estado de tu sesion para comprobar el funcionamiento de los tokens</p>
        </section>

        <div class="state-session">
            <p>Estado de la sesion
                <span id="state">
                    <% if(session) { %>Activa
                        <% } else { %>Inactiva<% } %>
                </span>
            </p>
        </div>

        <% if(!session) { %>
            <section class="inactive-session">
                <h3>Parece que no tienes una sesion activa</h3>
                <p>Inicia sesion para poder acceder a las funcionalidades de la pagina</p>
                <a id="btn-log" href="/login">Iniciar sesion</a>
            </section>
            <% } %>
    </main>

</body>

</html>